{"tid":1330035,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港要效法] 委內瑞拉警無預警下發橡膠子彈　示威少年臉部遭狂轟致雙目失明","createTime":"2019-07-18T11:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T22:32:29.000Z","uid":165620,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b44a4d0d767d49c2254fb9d250ead45643c266aa","tid":1330035,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:43:24.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉警無預警下發橡膠子彈　示威少年臉部遭狂轟致雙目失明<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/353431\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F353431&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE1I2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=2d713bcc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/353431</a><br />\n<br />\n19:30 Safari世界說<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉最近一場示威抗議引發暴力衝突，一名青少年遭52發子彈擊中臉部，其中16發打中眼睛造成失明。聯合國譴責委國政府違反人權，委國政府隨後立即發布調查報告，譴責兩名鎮壓警察。<br />\n<br />\n委國聖克里斯托瓦爾市（SanCristobal）市民7月2日上街遊行，抗議該地區家用煤氣短缺。不過卻遭警方無預警暴力鎮壓，使用橡膠子彈攻擊民眾，造成16歲的查孔（Rufo Chacon）雙眼失明。<br />\n<br />\n醫生表示，查孔被52發子彈擊中臉部，其中16發在眼查孔受傷前後照片（點圖放大）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/18/193644_f060807949997d6aa43690c0b758dff4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F18%2F193644_f060807949997d6aa43690c0b758dff4.png&h=a58ea043&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/18/193647_f28fa6025b1500911114911bae7d805c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F18%2F193647_f28fa6025b1500911114911bae7d805c.png&h=bb47f326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方調查報告顯示，該市警察無預警向民眾暴力施壓，其他兩名未成年抗議者頭部也受到傷害。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名是查孔14歲的弟弟阿德里他的頭部挨警相棍，當時他們與母親上街抗議該地區家用媒氣短缺，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（Adrian）安聯合國人權事務高級專員巴切萊特Bachelet）對此發表聲明，譴（Michelle責委內瑞拉政府「違反人權」委國總統馬杜羅（Nicolas Maduro）反駁說，報告不公允聯合國發出聲明數小時後，委內瑞拉政府隨即宣布，兩名警察因殺人未遂，使用武器不當，殘忍行為等遭起訴。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉西部長期來以反政府知名。2014年起，該地區發生過大大小小的暴力衝突，包含委國最大規模的幾件衝突。「我已經開始忘記查孔在示威抗議後表示，顏色是什麼了」，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「所有的政治家都是騙子，這裏的法律是用來攻擊市民而不是保護</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n將香港開槍射到人隻眼嘅新聞推上聯合國，推到警隊內控及割席</span></span>"},{"pid":"b1d3178fd36c17ffdac3d89477a77fa10cd0c849","tid":1330035,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:43:41.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"640b0037188bf0d1706690b9a9965f242733ba85","tid":1330035,"uid":60434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"聯合國對住中國就唔撚出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f53e91d0663e5a0da8f8f44f0a33c9828a1472f","tid":1330035,"uid":279525,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:45:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"689844d808e4493f624eb39f132429d3d2747637","tid":1330035,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"唔理你爭取咩先，你用暴力就一定錯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1329924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1329924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84070a7425bc33fc211729b1614adb2528e9d246","tid":1330035,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">急貼 連儂牆<br />\n重點 反警方暴力 濫權遊行 7.21，爭取中間派出來</span></span>"},{"pid":"84de752a941ab5523b6efb7a6cab8f116fe8d604","tid":1330035,"uid":165620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇到"},{"pid":"d2b6002e0779c5b05d0f